:

1. On je bio *takav* čovek da se uvek isticao. (He was such a man that he always stood out.)
2. *Takav* je bio naš stav prema situaciji. (That was our attitude towards the situation.)
3. To je bio *takav* događaj da će se dugo pamtiti. (It was such an event that it will be remembered for a long time.)
4. Ništa nije bilo *takvo* kakvo je trebalo da bude. (Nothing was such as it should have been.)
5. Ona je imala *takvu* igru da je pobedila. (She had such a game that she won.)